---------------
Gob Online Chat - Change Log
---------------

============
Version: 0.3
Date:

Features

* A progress bar is now presented while the applet is loading
* Re-arranged Package Name under sh.bob.gob  (see sf #830410)
* Created Common Regex Libs and utilised them in ClientCommand (see sf #830411)
* Server Configuration File 830828
* Debugging and Logging Runtime Configuration 830832
* XML Protocol Sub-system 830375
* Run as Windows Service 830890
* Provide MS Windows Installation 830889
* Room/Priv Activity Notification 830378
* Formatted Text - Colours etc. 830861
* Applet Window Resizing 830892
* Tab Close Button 830867
* Tab Close Button on Tab 830873
* Tab Icons 830851

Bugs

*

============
Version: 0.2
Date: 2003/10/25

Features

* Java Applet is now started in its own HTML window (see sf #688359)
* The lobby is now removed while disconnected (see sf #686540)
* Added support for user renaming (see sf #686542)
* Added support for private chat (see sf #688367)
* Added support for rooms (see sf #688363)
* Gob now loads "panels" for each tab, allowing a more modular configuration.
* There is a seperate Runnable class for the thread. 
* Documentation Updated.
* Server port is now set on the command line.

Bugs

* Fixed handling of failed connections, signups and selector registration. 
Now you don't need to hit disconnect yourself (see sf #686534).
* Will now handle the characters []\ in a message.

============